---
layout: layouts/page.njk
permalink: /code/
title: Code
---
<section>
  <h1>Code</h1>
  <p>
    For the Avanti Fellows ecosystem, browse the <a href="https://github.com/avantifellows/">GitHub organization</a>. 
    I help maintain Quiz Engine, Portal, Reporting Engine, Session Manager, and more. 
  </p>
  <p>
    These repos have a variety of open issues, many of which are beginner-friendly. 
    Please consider contributing! You can reach out to me on Avanti's Discord. 
    My discord id is <span style="font-family: Courier; font-size: 16px">suryabulusu</span>.
  </p>
</section>

<ul class="post-list">
  {% for repo in codeRepos | sort(attribute='published') | reverse %}
    <li class="post-item">
      <div class="post-meta">{{ repo.published | readableDate }}</div>
      <h2><a href="{{ repo.url }}">{{ repo.title }}</a></h2>
      <p>{{ repo.summary }}

        {% if repo.resources %}
          <span class="repo-resources">
            {% for resource in repo.resources %}
              <a href="{{ resource.url }}">{{ resource.label }}</a>{% if not loop.last %} ·{% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </span>
        {% endif %}
      </p>
      {% if repo.tags %}
        <div class="inline-tags">
          {% for tag in repo.tags %}
            <span>{{ tag }}</span>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
